result.name: Gaia Veggie Shop

reviews.text: Especially for oversea visitors to Hong Kong.... You need to come here and taste Chinese vegetarian food at their best.

Food is always taste the same. No surprises.
DO NOT expect any services！ 
They wont care about you.

This place has such great presentation with their food!  Their dishes look like "the real" thing.  They had a really nice taro fish, the pea sprouts were amazing and the "sashimi" was so good!  In fact, all their dishes were really good, I would love to go there or somewhere like this place again!  Please give this place try!

Glfidt time in this veggie house. Set lunch menu is of high value  - big portion and reasonable price. Afternoon tea set is also great. Lunch is busy and need advanced booking. Should visit again!

Dinner is also good. Don’t think too much - simply order the chef’s recommendations!
The variety of food is very good, the salad must be eaten, other Chinese dishes are very special to try, a very diverse Chinese vegetarian restaurant

result.name: Pioneer Centre Shopping Arcade

reviews.text:
Whether mornings, afternoons or evenings, it's a good place for a not-fancy get-together mall since it has a few restaurants which you can sit, eat and chat and no one will stare at you waiting for you to leave.

It's also a good place to walk around in cause it's got quite a few mobile carriers on the ground floor plus electronic shops on the 2nd floor.
A good variety of mobile phone peripherals, electronic gadgets, etc on sale.  A few cafes offer drinks and snacks if you get tired.
Good for electronics and great bag shop in 1st floor
Not as crowded as other shopping malls in Hong Kong. Easy shopping with some restaurants.
Pretty awesome discovery walking from Mong Kok to Prince Edward. Has shops from China mobile to most basic electronics, Remax and Starbucks with limited seats. if only a bit dated but with character.

result.name: 大自然素食

reviews.text:
好睇唔好食! 
沒有一個中心口味，油炸品有油“益”味。
不會再去，也不會推荐，是今天错误的選擇。
食物頗新穎，也算用心製作，衹是有些嘈！
價錢算中上,但味道好,純素很少,我一個人吃了一碟日本拉麵,一百蚊可有四蚊鷄回收,雜費已廿幾了,有少少赤!
Especially for oversea visitors to Hong Kong.... You need to come here and taste Chinese vegetarian food at their best.
